title: Supply and disposition of refined petroleum products, July 2015 (Statistics Canada)
text: ( Source : Statistics Canada ) Released : 2015-10-14 Refinery production 9.3 million cubic metres July 2015 -3.5% (12-month change) Refinery receipts increase Canadian refineries received 8.8 million cubic metres of crude oil in July, up 0.3%
